quran[27{c,v,t}:
68,16,anqareeb hum is ki soond par daagh lagayen ge
68,17,"hum ne inn ( ahal mecca ) ko usi terhan azmaish mein dala hai jis terhan aik baagh ke malikon ko azmaish mein dala tha, jab onhon ne qisam khayi ke subah saweray zaroor apne baagh ke phal torhin ge"
68,18,aur woh koi istanna nahi kar rahay thay
68,19,raat ko woh soye parre thay ke tumahray rab ki taraf se aik bulaa is baagh par phir gayi
68,20,aur uss ka haal aisa ho gaya jaisay kati hui fasal ho
68,21,subah unn logon ne aik dosray ko puraka
68,22,ke agar phal tornay hain to saweray saweray apni khaiti ki taraf nikal chalo
68,23,chunancha woh chal parre aur aapas mein chupkay chupkay kehte jatay thay
68,24,ke aaj koi maskeen tumahray paas baagh mein nah anay paye
68,25,woh kuch nah dainay ka faisla kiye hue subah saweray jaldi jaldi iss terhan wahan gay jaisay ke woh ( phal tornay par ) Qadir hain
68,26,"magar jab baagh ko dekha to kehnay lagey"" hum rasta bhool gay hain"
68,27,"nahi, balkay hum mahroom reh gay """
68,28,"unn mein jo sab se behtar aadmi tha uss ne kaha"" mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke tum tasbeeh kyun nahi karte? """
68,29,"o hay pukaar utthay pak hai hamara rab, waqai hum gunah gaar thay"
68,30,phir unn mein se har aik dosray ko malamat karne laga
68,31,"aakhir ko unhon ne kaha"" afsos hamaray haal par, be shak hum sarkash ho gay thay"
68,32,"baeed nahi ke hamara rab hamein badlay mein iss se behtar baagh ataa farmaiye, hum apne rab ki taraf rujoo karte hain """
68,33,"aisa hota hai azaab aur akhirat ka azaab iss se bhi bara hai, kash yeh log iss ko jantay"
68,34,yaqeenan khuda taras logon ke liye unn ke rab ke haan Nemat bhari jannaten hain
68,35,kya hum farmaa bardaroon ka haal mujrimon ka sa kar den ?
68,36,"tum logon ko kya ho gaya hai, tum kaisay hukum lagatay ho ?"
68,37,kya tumahray paas koi kitaab hai jis mein tum yeh parhte ho
68,38,ke tumahray liye zaroor wahan wohi kuch hai jo tum apne liye pasand karte ho ?
68,39,ya phir kya tumahray liye roz qayamat taq hum par kuch ehad o Paiman saabit hain ke tumhe wohi kuch miley ga jis ka tum hukum lagao ?
68,40,inn se pucho tum mein se kon iss ka zamin hai ?
68,41,ya phir inn ke tehra-ay hue kuch shareek hain ( jinhon ne iss ka zimma liya ho )? yeh baat hai to layein apne sharikon ko agar yeh sachey hain
68,42,jis roz sakht waqt aa parre ga aur logon ko sajda karne ke liye bulaya jaye ga to yeh log sajda nah kar saken ge
